Description:
-----------
This repo is contains a modified version of the Todo demo application originally written by Jérôme Gravel-Niquet and linked in the official Backbone.js website (http://documentcloud.github.com/backbone/).  

The goal was to use Require.js (http://requirejs.org/) to organize the code into separate javascript code that resembles the approach taken by traditional Object Oriented programming styles especially given the MVC framework provided by Backbone.js.

